    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 given medium model influence and high decision consequence. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met across all five flow-speed combinations.",
